  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation et Nepomuk-core</title>

    <para>Installez <application>nepomuk-core</application> en lancant les commandes suivantes:</para>

<!-- Nothing is installed in sysconfdir ... -->
<screen><userinput>mkdir build &amp;&amp;
cd build &amp;&amp;
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=&kde-dir; -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release .. &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

  <para> Ce paquet n'a pas de suite de tests. </para>
  <para>Maintenant, en tant qu'utilisateur <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>&nbsp;:</para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

